snippet.title: Colorfiction - The Sands of Voltark -  Trailer II
snippet.description:
Upon crash landing on this desert planet you have the choice to explore its beautiful steppes or systematically stripmine its resources. Choose wisely..
Play the beta at: https://colorfiction.itch.io/voltark

Stay up with updates on: https://twitter.com/colorfiction
